### 6. **Core Merge Functions (Pattern for Image+Text Integration)**

**File:** `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775497486932-ghvfn2/src/models.js` (lines 636-698)

