This file is auto-discovered by the `collect_and_execute_pipeline_tests()` function in `tests/test_utils.js` (line 121), which reads every `.js` file in `tests/pipelines/`. No registration is needed.

The test file should follow the exact pattern of `tests/pipelines/test_pipelines_image_to_text.js`:

