    },
```

`onnx-community/SmolVLM-256M-Instruct` is the smallest production-quality VLM available as ONNX on the Hub, backed by `SmolVLMForConditionalGeneration` which is in `MODEL_FOR_IMAGE_TEXT_TO_TEXT_MAPPING_NAMES`.

